    "description": "Torex Semiconductor Ltd. researches, develops, manufactures, and sells IC and active discrete components in Japan, Asia, Europe, and North America. The company offers DC/DC converters, voltage regulators, voltage detectors/reset Ics, push button controllers, load switches, PLL clock generators, transient voltage suppressors, MOSFET, power devices SiC-SBD, and power MOSFET; charge pump, battery charge, and hall ICs; and Shottky barrier, Zener, switching, and bridge diodes. Its products are used in industrial, consumer electronics, medical and healthcare, automotive, and computer and communications fields. Torex Semiconductor Ltd. was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
